# Alcohol

Alcohol - PH359

## Requirements

[Docker](https://docs.docker.com/install/) and [CWLTool](https://github.com/common-workflow-language/cwltool#install)

## Configuration

Specify input dataset path in [Alcohol-inputs.yml](Alcohol-inputs.yml).

## Usage

Run: `cwltool Alcohol.cwl Alcohol-inputs.yml`
